{"type":null,"faqId":31624,"title":"How do I unlock my P8 directly using the TalkBand B2?","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 0.9111111in 1.25in 1.0in 1.25in;}\n.p1{text-indent:0.33333334in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:Times New Roman;font-size:12pt;}\n.s1{font-weight:bold;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span>1. Pair your phone with the TalkBand B2. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>2. On your phone, touch </span><span class=\"s1\">Settings</span><span> &gt;</span><span class=\"s1\"> Screen lock &amp; passwords </span><span>&gt;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"s1\">Smart unlock</span><span>, and set the screen unlock pattern and passcode. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>3. Return to the Settings screen, touch </span><span class=\"s1\">Security </span><span>&gt; </span><span class=\"s1\">Trusted agents</span><span>, and enable Smart unlock. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span> 4. Touch </span><span class=\"s1\">Add a Bluetooth device</span><span> and select the TalkBand B2 for smart unlock. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>5. Press the power button to lock the screen, and turn on the screen to check whether an unlock pattern is required. </span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span>When your TalkBand B2 is within range, turn on the phone screen and slide to unlock your phone without a passcode. </span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":339,"faqType":"Miscellaneous","useful":15,"unUseful":5,"languageId":1,"languageName":"en","faqCode":"6124","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Others","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1435059513000,"seriesProductName":"B2","visitedTimes":1169,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null